section_title: Matters Relating to the International Transaction Log (ITL)
sentences: This item (FCCC/SBI/2015/INF.2) was first considered on Monday, 1 June.
Chair Yauvoli proposed, and parties agreed to, informal consultations facilitated by Yuji Mizuno (Japan).
During the SBI closing plenary on Thursday, 11 June, the SBI adopted conclusions.
